## What you need to modify

Your project has 7 files. You only need to care about 3:

| File | What it does | When to edit |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| `src/routers/api.py` | API endpoints | **Every time** |
| `tests/test_api.py` | Tests for endpoints | **Every time** |
| `src/core/database.py` | DB setup (models, connection) | When adding models |
| `src/schemas.py` | Pydantic schemas | When adding schemas |
| Others (Dockerfile, CI config, .env) | Project infra | Almost never |

## Quick Start

```bash
cp .env.example .env
pip install -e ".[dev]"
uvicorn src.main:app --reload
```

Open [http://localhost:8000/docs](http://localhost:8000/docs) for Swagger UI.

