## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Framework | FastAPI |
| ORM | SQLAlchemy 2.0 (async) |
| Migrations | Alembic |
| Database | PostgreSQL (asyncpg) |
| Validation | Pydantic v2 + pydantic-settings |
| Testing | pytest + httpx |
| Linting | Ruff (E, W, F, I, N, UP, B, C4, ARG) |
| Type Checking | mypy (strict) |

